### POST /chat
AI chatbot endpoint.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "message": "Can I buy a phone?",
  "lang": "en"
}
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "reply": "Based on your finances, you CAN consider buying a phone IF your savings are above 20%...",
  "intent": "buy_phone",
  "lang": "en",
  "savings_context": 37.0
}
```

**Supported chat questions:**
- "Can I buy a phone?" / "क्या फोन खरीद सकता हूं?"
- "How to save money?" / "पैसे कैसे बचाएं?"
- "How to invest?" / "निवेश कैसे करें?"
- "Tell me about budget rules"
- "About EMI" / "Can I buy a bike/car/laptop?"

