## 💡 AI Insight Logic

The insight engine uses industry-standard financial benchmarks:

| Savings Rate | Status    | Action |
|-------------|-----------|--------|
| > 30%       | Excellent | Invest surplus |
| 20–30%      | Good      | Push to 30% |
| 10–20%      | Average   | Reduce expenses |
| < 10%       | Critical  | Urgent action needed |

**Expense thresholds:**
- Food > 30% of income → High alert
- Rent > 35% of income → High alert
- Entertainment > 10% → Reduce leisure
- Shopping > 15% → Budget rule suggested

